steps.body:
Akamai Functions ships with a built-in KV store accessible via the Spin SDK in any supported language:

```
let store = Store::open_default()?;
store.set("user:42", b"{\"plan\":\"pro\"}")?;
let val = store.get("user:42")?;
```

Key features:
- Globally readable from any Function instance
- Per-component isolation (one Function can't read another's keys without a binding)
- Designed for read-heavy workloads (redirects, feature flags, configuration, session lookups)
